FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_info mi
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.kind_id  =  3 AND t.production_year  =  1996 AND ci.person_id  <  982926 AND ci.role_id  <  2 AND mi.info_type_id  <  66
